title: How to Draw an Eyebrow

steps.headline: Draw a curve line above the eye.
Add a thicker rugged line following the form of the curved line drawn previously.
Draw a curve line above the eye.
Based on the curved line drawn previously, draw lines to add volume to the eyebrow.

text: A Realistic Eyebrow Draw a curve line above the eye.  Add a thicker rugged line following the form of the curved line drawn previously.  A Cartoon Eyebrow Draw a curve line above the eye.  Based on the curved line drawn previously, draw lines to add volume to the eyebrow.  Color your eyebrow.
